  speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 256f31eac24b8a44c959cc945a4769a8, type: 2}
  textLine:
  - "Welcome! Potions, weapons, charms\u2014all here. Your gold keeps you alive."
  - This elven blade cuts through shadows. Expensive, but worth it.
  - Crystal Cave gem? 800 gold. It's cracked, but I'll take the risk.
  - "Stock up for the night. Bring back curiosities\u2014I pay well. Stay safe."
